headline: APA Corporation: An Interesting Proxy For Suriname Working Interests But Not Much Else (Rating Downgrade)
summary: APA Corporation had strong FCF in Q4 but faces weaker oil prices in 2025. Learn why APA stock remains a hold due to robust dividends and Suriname risks.
